    <item>
      <title>美国银行强制美国员工将工作场所纠纷提交仲裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/bofa-compels-us-staff-to-take-workplace-disputes-to-arbitration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行公司将要求其美国员工将几乎所有法律纠纷都提交私人仲裁，加入华尔街同行的行列，寻求在公众视线之外解决工作场所冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/bofa-compels-us-staff-to-take-workplace-disputes-to-arbitration</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 18:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>红色浪潮增加达成协议的可能性，债务上限紧张局势有望缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/debt-limit-ructions-seen-easing-as-red-wave-boosts-odds-of-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些华尔街策略师表示，一个可能统一的美国政府可能会使在财政部借款权限耗尽之前更容易达成暂停或提高债务上限的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/debt-limit-ructions-seen-easing-as-red-wave-boosts-odds-of-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:55:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥比索因莱特希泽将领导美国贸易政策的报告而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/mexican-peso-slumps-on-report-lighthizer-to-lead-us-trade-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在《金融时报》报道罗伯特·莱特希泽被唐纳德·特朗普新政府任命为美国贸易代表后，墨西哥比索扩大下跌。]]></description>
